rows.label: qst200204_msg0004
rows.name:
Tell us everything you know
about Harghal!

rows.label: qst200204_msg0006
rows.name: ...Sorry, but I can't help you there.

rows.label: qst200204_msg0007
rows.name:
We heard the two of you were
the best of friends, though.

rows.label: qst200204_msg0008
rows.name:
I don't know who told you that
nonsense, but believe me, I'm not
friends with that woman.

rows.label: qst200204_msg0009
rows.name:
Now if you're not customers, could
you get going? You're getting in the
way of my work.

rows.label: qst200204_msg0010
rows.name: Why are you so afraid to talk?

rows.label: qst200204_msg0011
rows.name:
I'm not afraid. I just don't want to
think about that traitor!

rows.label: qst200204_msg0012
rows.name:
She was an incredible dancer -
everyone's darling, Bahn's favorite.

rows.label: qst200204_msg0013
rows.name:
And then she betrayed me and just left!
Is that something a friend would do?!

rows.label: qst200204_msg0014
rows.name:
This doesn't seem like it's going to be
straightforward. What should we do?

rows.label: qst200204_msg0016
rows.name:
Leave it to me!
I'll talk some sense into her!
